### Hadith 4:503

*Narrated Ibn 'Abbas:*

The Prophet said, "If anyone of you, on having sexual relation with his
wife, says: 'O Allah! Protect me from Satan, and prevent Satan from
approaching the offspring you are going to give me,' and if it happens
that the lady conceives a child, Satan will neither harm it nor be given
power over it."

